<h3 id="a11y">Accessibility</h3>
<p>Use <code>aria-label</code> and <code>title</code> when the Tag only contains an icon:</p>
<code-sample>
  <mw-chip kind="suggestion" title="free breakfast" aria-label="free breakfast"><mw-icon name="bakery_dining"></mw-icon></mw-chip>
</code-sample>
